data.description: Desirable 4 BED 2.5 BA, two story on a large fenced corner lot! As you enter the home, you are greeted by the foyer W/high ceilings offering an abundance of natural light. Enjoy entertaining & relaxing in the family room complete w/heated engineered HDWD floors, your feet will be toasty on cold winter nights! The dining room works well for formal gatherings or as a home office. Amenities to appreciate in the eat-in kitchen include, crisp white cabinets, SS appliances & gas stove. Main flr primary suite complete w/spa-like bath offering dual sink vanity, WIC & spacious separate shower. Three additional good sized bedrooms along with bath featuring dual sinks & tub/shower are located on the upper level. Easy outdoor entertaining on the patio! VA Buyers have the opportunity to assume current mortgage at 4.25%
